  "title": "Temp Admin (Legal) @ Toa Payoh",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Scope:</strong></p><ul><li>Work with the relevant teams such as lease issuing bank loan team , lease issuing concessionary rate loan team, refinancing and  lease buy-back team  and the title search team and carry out such processes as may be required to ensure that instruments are prepared with 100 % accuracy and that title searches are conducted comprehensively.</li><li>In the course of preparation of legal instruments, to also work with internal stakeholders and liaise with external stakeholders like IRAS for stamping matters and Singapore Land Authority for registration matters .</li><li>Carry out other administrative and ad-hoc duties such as printing, filing, posting documents and despatch.</li><li>Besides issuance of the leases, you need assistance for doing other duties, e.g. carrying of boxes for off-site/disposal/sealing of the documents.</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Working Hours:</strong><br />Mondays to Thursdays: 8.30am to 6.00pm<br />Fridays: 8.30am to 5.30pm<br /><br /><strong>Salary: </strong>$15/hour<br /><strong>Contract Period: </strong>3 months to 1 year<br /><br />EA License No: 96C4864<br />Reg. No.: R24121728 EUNICE WOO JING QI</p>",
